EverWell: Self-Care and Scratch Art


Posted on November 02, 2022




Share this on Facebook








Share this on Twitter












By: UIC Students in partnership with UIC Wellness Center
What is self-care?

Self-care is the practice of actively promoting our happiness, looking out for our own well-being, and being able to respond to stressful situations without becoming unbalanced or experiencing a health emergency.
To learn more about...

What is self-care
Why is self-care important
Different types of self-care
Self-care for college students
